{
  "argument_loc": "Unspecified",
  "description": "Sets the selection state of the given row of the given listbox of style LB_MULTI.\nThe command has to be called for every row which is needed to be selected in multi-selection listbox. Use negative index -1 to select/deselect all rows (since {{GVI|arma3|2.12}}).\nFor single selection listbox use [[lbSetCurSel]] instead.",
  "effect_loc": "Unspecified",
